4.  **Upload the code**: Upload the modified code to the Arduino board using the Arduino IDE.
5.  **Test the system**: Put the sensor on hot and cold surfaces to test the accuracy of the temperature reading. Adjust the potentiometer to control the brightness of the LCD display.
